sentences: Letitia Jane Dean (born 14 November 1967) is an English actress known for her portrayal of Sharon Watts in the BBC soap opera, EastEnders.
An original cast member from 1985 to 1995, she reprised the role from 2001 to 2006, and again from 2012.
